modName: Freya - A Beautiful Nord Savegame - DELETED
summary: Beautiful Nord Freya, originally my first character, now made available to you. This lvl 1 savegame starts just before stepping to the chopping block, for maximum story involvement.
descriptionHtml:
In reaction to my pinup pictures, I have recently been asked to make a savegame out of my first main character. Seeing that people liked the way original Freya Urleif looked, I have now done so.
The level 1 character, now simply named \"Freya\", starts out right before stepping toward the chopping block in Helgen, just to add that little bit of in medias res feeling for you ;) 

You have the ultimate choice: What will her destiny be, her actions, her specialties, her weaknesses and most importantly, her past. All that is up to your imagination...

There are a few mods required to establish the exact look that Freya has in the pictures (and maybe in your hearts, who knows). These mods are listed in the \"required files\" menu (the floppy disc icon below the mod\'s statistics).

BTW, if you prefer any other body mod than LFF, you can of course use that ;)

Credits to MrFunseth for suggesting I upload Freya as a savegame variant ;)
author: MnNwr
